OL,6,FThe 2 year trial, taking place in 6
OL,7,Fschools in Liverpool, is the first of
OL,8,Fits kind in the UK. Holy Family
OL,9,FCatholic High School is one of the
OL,10,Fschools to take part in the lessons
OL,11,Fthat are taught by .
OL,13,FOne of the 3 Dads, Mike Palmer from
OL,14,FSale - whose daughter Beth took her
OL,15,Fown life four years ago - was there
OL,16,Ffor the lesson and is on the steering
OL,17,Fgroup of the trial. He said:
