OL,6,F"There is always the chance that it
OL,7,Fcould have made a difference with
OL,8,FBeth, if Beth had been more ware and I
OL,9,Fhad been more aware, what we are
OL,10,Fteaching these kids now they will take
OL,11,Finto adulthood they will take into
OL,12,Fparenthood and there is always a
OL,13,Fchance that Bethy would still be here"
