OL,3,CMerseyside schools the first to trial
OL,4,Cnew suicide prevention lessons
OL,6,FThe trial is being run by and is based
OL,7,Fon a programme called MAPSS already
OL,8,Fbeing used in Australia. Year 10
OL,9,Fstudents are taught how to spot the
OL,10,Fsigns of suicide and how to get help,
OL,11,Fthey are also screened and those
OL,12,Fidentified as high risk are offered an
OL,13,F8 week course of support.
OL,15,FThis randomised control trial by
OL,16,FLiverpool John Moores University is
OL,17,Fthe first of its kind in the UK,
OL,18,Ffunded by the government, it will look
OL,19,Fat the safety of the lessons and
OL,20,Fwhether they're effective.
