OL,6,FLucy Skillen is the Pastoral Manager
OL,7,Fand Mental Health lead at Holy Family
OL,8,FCatholic High, she said:
OL,10,F"It is a real worry, we tend to have a
OL,11,Flot more who are self harming and
OL,12,Ftherefore are at risk of suicide, we
OL,13,Fhave noticed it in our upper years for
OL,14,Fquite a few years, but we are now
OL,15,Fstarting to see a large proportion
OL,16,Fcoming in from Primary School"
