OL,4,Cnew suicide prevention lessons
OL,6,FMike Palmer believes the programme
OL,7,Fwill save lives, he said "To teach our
OL,8,Fchildren the life skills in keeping
OL,9,Fthemselves safe and this MAPSS
OL,10,Fprogramme is exactly the sort of thing
OL,11,Fwe are looking at, it is a whole
OL,12,Fschool approach bringing in teaching
OL,13,Fstaff and parents and it is a whole
OL,14,Fsocietal change"
OL,16,FThe Government are yet to decide
OL,17,Fwhether to add suicide prevention to
OL,18,Fthe curriculum, but the findings of
OL,19,Fthis 2-year trial could help inform
OL,20,Fthat decision.
